org.apache.pdfbox.io

Interface RandomAccessRead

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    RandomAccess
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RandomAccessReadBuffer, RandomAccessReadBufferedFile, RandomAccessReadMemoryMappedFile, RandomAccessReadView, SequenceRandomAccessRead

    public interface RandomAccessRead
extends Closeable
    An interface allowing random access read operations.
